///Main Structure of Backend\\\

index.js is main file
Using Module way in our application
Storing database info in env such as URL for database

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


///Full Project Structure\\\
We will be using MCV structure
---------------------------------------------------------------------
Controllers will have the logic
---------------------------------------------------------------------
index.js will have all the trigger points and will go to routing folder where i will have routes
Models will have my Basic Models
---------------------------------------------------------------------
Utils folder will have al the functions that we will be using again and again, eg used for outsourcing reusable code
---------------------------------------------------------------------
in the modals folder i have user.js modal which has the basic user schema with all datatypes we will be using
I also used roles schema under Role.js that will have an id and a name which willl bascially have the roles such as admin, users etc and will be bind and create a reationship to the user schema
---------------------------------------------------------------------
using bcrypt in Auth.controller.js for hashing the password when registering a user inside register function
using bcrypt.compare in Auth.controller.js for logging in when loggin in
---------------------------------------------------------------------
inside utils.js we have the success and error messages middleware handeling and providing errors alll over the application
---------------------------------------------------------------------
in UserToken,js in modals we have the schema for storing User tokens




--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
//Front end Details\\\

Using Tailwind on the frontend for styles
Components folder will have all the shared components
Pages folderwill have all pages like login page, signup page etc
---------------------------------------------------------------------
Using newer method of injecting services e.j router = inject(Router) so no longer to add services to constructor
Sercices folder will have the all the outsourced code
Validate folder folder will have custom validators
---------------------------------------------------------------------
Using Angular/Material Snackbar to display notifications
---------------------------------------------------------------------
Dashboard in pages will have our home page when logged in
Created a custom validator in validators folder to validate that the password and confirm password match
---------------------------------------------------------------------
In Auth service i am handling Authorizations like register login and forgot password
It only contains the requests, requests URLS are inside api.ur;.ts file
---------------------------------------------------------------------
custom Snackbar service that displays notifications effectively like when a user is successfully logged in
---------------------------------------------------------------------
Displaying span error messages after inputs for duplicate username and email in the registration.ts
